# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.2.0] - 2025-10-29
### Added
- Toggle to **hide/show filters** in Browse.
- Larger/more visible **Concentration and Ritual Pills**.

### Improved
- **Level (Magic/Characteristic)** filters display **only levels with data**.
- **Layout revamp** in Browse (readability and focus).

### Fixed
- –

## [1.1.0] - 2025-10-28
### Added
- Components pill: V/S/M grouped into **one** pill, with the material displayed in full in "M".
- Print: Component pill parity in preview/print.
- Rich text on cards/print: support for paragraphs (`\n\n`), **bold**, and *italics*.

### Changed
- Visualization of component chips and the container (slight distinction from other pills).

### Fixed
- Tags: Refined `buff` heuristic to avoid false positives in text like "damage increases" (e.g., *Acid Splash*). JSON tags remain the source of truth.
- Hydration: Avoids `<p>` nested within `<p>` when wrapping the body in `<div>`.

### Docs
- Added `.markdownlint.json` and `.markdownlintignore`; Markdown lint fixes.

## [1.0.0] - 2025-10-28
### Added
- Unified browser (Spells + Features) with clickable pills and PT/EN search.
- Packs persisted in IndexedDB (offline-ready).
- Print Builder: drag-and-drop reordering, 1–2 columns, front/back with mirroring.
- Global preferences (PT/EN language and light/dark/system theme).
- PWA manifest, theme-color, and icons; offline installation and use.

### Improved
- General layout (chips, card grid, floating dock).
- Accessibility: visible focus, skip-to-content, aria labels, and aria-live.
- Print styles (hyphenation, spacing, repeated header).

### Fixed
- Contrast and readability in dark mode (chips, tabs, dock).
- Filtering by tags and visual duplication anomalies.

